Your tasks for Step 1:

1. Read the full lead JSON below.
2. Read the raw outreach prompt provided by the User.
3. Based on the lead and company data, decide which data points are most relevant to make the prompt stronger and more specific. Include Fit Signals, Signal type and recommended messaging angle based on the news/specific business information. Prefer signals relevant to acquisition criteria such as:  
  -- Longevity / years in business  
  -- Reputation and customer relationships  
  -- Proven track record or stability  
  -- Company size (if available: revenue, employees)  
  -- Distinctive service offerings or special expertise (from keywords/news)  
4. Rewrite and structure the user’s raw prompt (if exists) so it is clear, focused, and ready for Step 2.
5. Ignore the parameter "Test Lead" in Lead JSON. Focus on personalization parameters.


